ieee_test_0 = {
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_1

    set_temp_variable = { to_bitwise_input = 998445.679 }
    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_bitwise = yes

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_1
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_1 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = {
                check_variable = { temp_array_0^num = temp_array_1^num }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    for_loop_effect = {
        start = 0
        end = 32
        compare = less_than
        value = idx

        if = {
            limit = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { temp_array_0^idx = temp_array_1^idx } }
            }
            set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
    }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_bitwise #0 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_bitwise #0 - PASS"
    }
    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    log = "Actual: [debug_print_array_id]"
    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 1 }
    log = "Expect: [debug_print_array_id]"

    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_1
}

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    store_bitwise = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_output = 998445.679 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { store_bitwise_output = expected_output } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - store_bitwise #0 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - store_bitwise #0 - PASS"
    }
    log = "Actual: [?store_bitwise_output]"
    log = "Expect: [?expected_output]"

    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -3 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #0 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #0 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}
ieee_test_4 = {
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_pdxvar = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_output = 0.004 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_overflow_flag =  0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag =       0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag =       0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { to_pdxvar_output = expected_output } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_overflow_flag = expected_overflow_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { to_pdxvar_output = expected_output } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_pdxvar #0 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_pdxvar #0 - PASS"
    }

    log = "Actual: [?to_pdxvar_output] overflow: [?ieee_overflow_flag] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "Expect: [?expected_output] overflow: [?expected_overflow_flag] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"

    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}
ieee_test_5 = {
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    
    set_temp_variable = { arg_a = 998445.679 }

    float_to_pdxvar = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_output = 0.004 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_overflow_flag =  0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag =       0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag =       0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { out_a = expected_output } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { overflow_flag = expected_overflow_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - float_to_pdxvar #0 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - float_to_pdxvar #0 - PASS"
    }

    log = "Actual: [?out_a] overflow: [?ieee_overflow_flag] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "Expect: [?expected_output] overflow: [?expected_overflow_flag] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
}

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -3 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #1 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #1 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #2 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #2 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -2 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #3 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #3 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -2 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #4 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #4 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -2 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #5 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #5 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #6 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #7 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #7 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #8 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #8 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #9 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #9 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #10 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #10 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #11 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #11 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #12 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #12 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #13 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #13 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -1 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #14 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #14 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #15 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #15 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #16 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #16 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #17 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #17 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #20 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #20 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #21 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #21 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #22 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #22 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val

    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #25 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #25 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #26 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                }
            }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #27 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #27 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {

                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #28 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #28 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

    }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {

                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #29 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #29 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                }
            }
