        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #30 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #30 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

            OR = {

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #31 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #31 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #32 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #32 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #33 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #33 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #34 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #34 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #35 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #35 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #36 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #36 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #37 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #37 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #38 - PASS"

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #40 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #40 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #41 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #41 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #42 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #42 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 2 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #43 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #43 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 2 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #44 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #44 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                }

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #45 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #46 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #46 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #47 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                }
            }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #49 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #49 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #50 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #50 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #51 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #51 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #52 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #52 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #53 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #53 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #54 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #54 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #56 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

                    array = expected_ieee_out_array

                }
            }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #57 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #57 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

        value = val

    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag =       0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag =       0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { out_a = expected_output } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { overflow_flag = expected_overflow_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #60 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }

    }

            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #61 - FAIL"

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #61 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                }
            }

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #62 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }

    }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #63 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #63 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    to_digit_array = yes

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #64 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #64 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #65 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val

    }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 4 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #66 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #66 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 4 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #67 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #67 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #68 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #68 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 5 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #70 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #70 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }

    }

            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #71 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #71 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }

    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }

    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #72 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }

    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #73 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #73 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

        value = val

    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
