    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 5 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #74 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #74 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #75 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #75 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }

    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #76 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #77 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #77 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 5 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #78 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #78 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #79 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #80 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #80 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #81 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #81 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #82 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #82 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #83 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #83 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #84 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #84 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #87 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val

    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #88 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #88 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }

    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #89 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #89 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 8 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #90 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #90 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }

                }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #91 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #94 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #94 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #95 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #95 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }

        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #97 - PASS"
    }

        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #98 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #98 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }

                }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #99 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #99 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val

    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #102 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #102 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        value = val

    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 6 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #103 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #103 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = -4 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #104 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #104 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 9 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #105 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #105 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }

    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #108 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #108 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 6 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #109 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #109 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 6 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }

            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #110 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #110 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { temp_array_0 = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { temp_array_id = 0 }
    to_digit_array = yes

    set_temp_variable = { expected_ieee_out_power = 6 }
    clear_temp_array = expected_ieee_out_array
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 4 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #111 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #111 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #112 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #112 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #113 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #113 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 7 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #114 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #114 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

                }

        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }

        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #115 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #115 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }

            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }

        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }

        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #116 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #116 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"

    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 8 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 1 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #117 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #117 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}

    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 0 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 3 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 1 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 2 }
    add_to_temp_array = { expected_ieee_out_array = 5 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_sign_bit = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_inf_flag = 0 }
    set_temp_variable = { expected_nan_flag = 0 }

    set_temp_variable = { invalid = 0 }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { io_error_flag > 0 }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^num = expected_ieee_out_array^num } }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_power = expected_ieee_out_power } }
                any_of = {
                    array = expected_ieee_out_array
                    index = idx

                    NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_out_array^idx = expected_ieee_out_array^idx } }
                }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            OR = {
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_inf_flag = expected_inf_flag } }
                NOT = { check_variable = { ieee_nan_flag = expected_nan_flag } }
            }
        }
        set_temp_variable = { invalid = 1 }
    }
    if = {
        limit = {
            check_variable = { invalid = 1 }
        }
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #118 - FAIL"
        add_to_temp_array = { test_fail_array = test_id }
    }
    else = {
        log = "Test [?test_id] - to_digit_array #118 - PASS"
    }

    for_each_loop = {
        array = ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = ieee_sign_bit }
    log = "Actual: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?ieee_out_power] inf: [?ieee_inf_flag] nan: [?ieee_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"

    for_each_loop = {
        array = expected_ieee_out_array
        value = val
        
        add_to_temp_array = { to_print_array = val }
    }
    set_temp_variable = { print_sign_bit = expected_sign_bit }
    log = "Expect: [ieee_minus_decider]10^[?expected_ieee_out_power] inf: [?expected_inf_flag] nan: [?expected_nan_flag]"
    log = "[debug_print_array]"
    
    set_temp_variable = { io_error_flag = 0 }
    clear_temp_array = temp_array_0
}
